{FFFFFFFF|Full Bloom}
Your next Wild Growth applies Lifebloom to all targets at {3}% effectiveness. Lasts for {4} sec.

Casting {1} Starfires empowers Wrath for {2} sec. Casting {3} Wraths empowers Starfire for {4} sec.

|T236152:24|t {ffffffff|Eclipse (Solar)}
